# Radio / Checkbox / Toggle

**Figma:** [Radio / Checkbox / Toggle](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=128-10423&p=f&m=dev)

Radio, checkbox, toggle specs, states, and sizes below are derived from Figma node 128:10423.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Unselected border | `--border-base-default` |
| Selected fill | `--bg-brand-default` |
| Selected border | `--border-brand-default` |
| Checkmark | `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Track off | `--bg-base-tertiary` |
| Track on | `--bg-brand-default` |
| Handle | `--bg-base-default` |
| Label | `--text-base-default` |

---

## Radio Button

| State | Border | Fill |
|-------|--------|------|
| Unselected | `--border-base-default` | Transparent |
| Selected | `--border-brand-default` | `--bg-brand-default` |

- **Size:** ≥20px; 40×40px click target.
- **Label:** `--text-base-default`; Space/200 from control.

---

## Checkbox

| State | Border | Fill |
|-------|--------|------|
| Unselected | `--border-base-default` | Transparent |
| Selected | `--border-brand-default` | `--bg-brand-default`; `--text-brand-on-brand` checkmark |
| Indeterminate | Per Figma | Half fill |

- **Radius:** Radius/100 (4px).
- **Size:** ≥20px; 40×40px click target.

---

## Toggle Switch

| State | Track | Handle |
|-------|-------|--------|
| Off | `--bg-base-tertiary` | `--bg-base-default` circle, Shadow sm |
| On | `--bg-brand-default` | Same |

- **Radius:** Radius/Full or pill (9999px).
- **Size:** ~40×24px track; handle ≥20px.

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 128:10423.
